==選手概況和成績==
富赫·塞米（Fuahea Semi）是唯一一位代表湯加出戰本屆冬季奧運會的運動員。在2010年，他本有機會參加[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會|當屆在溫哥華舉行的冬季奧運會]]，但由於在賽前的資格賽發生意外而未能出線<ref>[http://www.radioaustralianews.net.au/stories/201002/2807009.htm?desktop "Tongan athlete narrowly misses out on Winter Olympics"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.radioaustralianews.net.au/stories/201002/2807009.htm?desktop |date=20110717125436 }} Australian Broadcasting Corporation 2010 2 1</ref>。2012年，他為賺取贊助費，而改名為德國內衣品牌布魯諾·巴納尼（Bruno Banani）<ref>[http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/Luge+hoaxster+name+change+legal+just+wants+race+Tonga+Sochi+Olympics/7906874/story.html "Luge ‘hoaxster’ name change now legal, just wants to race for Tonga at Sochi Olympics"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/Luge+hoaxster+name+change+legal+just+wants+race+Tonga+Sochi+Olympics/7906874/story.html |date=20140330185807 }} Vancouver Sun 2013 2 1</ref>。[[國際奧委會|國際奧委會]]副會長[[托馬斯·巴赫|托馬斯·巴赫]]因而批評這「很沒有品」<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/11/luge-tonga-sponsor-idUSL5E8DB0IF20120211 "Luge-Tongan changes name to brand in bid for Olympic glory"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/11/luge-tonga-sponsor-idUSL5E8DB0IF20120211 |date=20131020134841 }} Reuters 2012 2 11</ref>。

